1-in-memory DataBase(apache derby) + JPA  (Rest APi CURD Operation)

25-06-2018
----------
2- Rest API Request Validation













Request URL 
=============

Create Ticket
---------------
POST-http://localhost:8081/ticketBookingApp/ticket

{
"passengerName":"black",
"sourceStation":"pune",
"destStation":"mp",
"email":"th@gmail1.com"
}



Get All Ticket
---------------
GET-http://localhost:8081/ticketBookingApp/ticket



Get Ticket BY ID
-----------------
GET-http://localhost:8081/ticketBookingApp/ticket/5



Update Ticket
---------------
PUT-http://localhost:8081/ticketBookingApp/ticket

{
   "ticketId": 1,
   "passengerName": "black1",
   "bookingDate": 1529672698686,
   "sourceStation": "pune99",
   "destStation": "mp1",
   "email": "th@gmail1.com"
 }



Delete Ticket BY ID
--------------------
DELETE-http://localhost:8081/ticketBookingApp/ticket/1







